These are Puzzles for 2x3 Level 1

.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-1-1::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: almond-milk, coffee, juice
The people grow 3 different varities of flowers: rose, balloon-flower, daisy
1. the person who growsballoon-flower is in the middle##1
2. the person drinking juice is the person who growsdaisy##1
3. the person drinking almond-milk is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |      1      |   2    |    3    |
| Beverage   | almond-milk | coffee | juice   |
| Flower      | rose    | balloon-flower  | daisy |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-1-2::.
The people have 3 different jobs:  nurse, scientist, dressmaker
There are 3 different nationalities: argentine, canadian, nigerian
1. the argentine is on the left of the dressmaker##1
2. the canadian is on the far left##1
3. the canadian is the scientist##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2     |    3     |
| Job      | scientist | nurse     | dressmaker      |
| Nationality   | canadian | argentine | nigerian |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-1-3::.
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: r&b, house, disco
There 3 different types of food: plum, radish, raspberry
1. the fan of house is on the right of the person eating radish##1
2. the fan of disco is on the left of the person eating raspberry##1
3. the fan of r&b is on the left of the person eating radish##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1     |   2    |     3     |
| Music-Genre   | r&b | disco  | house       |
| Food       | plum     | radish | raspberry |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-1-4::.
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: indie, funk, pop
The people have 3 different hobbies: card-games, puzzles, woodworking
1. the fan of funk is on the right of the person who's hobby is woodworking##1
2. the fan of indie is on the right of the person who's hobby is card-games##1
3. the person who's hobby is woodworking is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1      |     2      |      3      |
| Music-Genre    | pop    | funk     | indie |
| Hobby   | woodworking | card-games | puzzles     |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-1-5::.
The people have 3 different hobbies: card-games, photography, skydiving
The people use 3 different means of transport: airplane, trike, van
1. the person driving the trike is the person who's hobby is skydiving##1
2. the person driving the trike is on the right of the person who's hobby is card-games##1
3. the person who's hobby is skydiving is on the right of the person driving the airplane##1
4. the person who's hobby is card-games is in the middle##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1      |    2     |    3     |
| Hobby         | photography | card-games     | skydiving |
| Transport   | van        | airplane | trike    |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-1-6::.
The people's birthday is in 3 different months: february, november, may
The people use 3 different means of transport: boat, motorbike, train
1. the person who's birthday is in february is on the right of the person driving the boat##1
2. the person who's birthday is in november is on the right of the person driving the motorbike##1
3. the person who's birthday is in may is the person driving the boat##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1      |     2     |   3   |
| Birthday        | may | february      | november  |
| Transport   | boat       | motorbike | train |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-1-7::.
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: jazz, r&b, salsa
The people's birthday is in 3 different months: june, january, july
1. the fan of salsa is on the left of the fan of jazz##1
2. the fan of r&b is the person who's birthday is in january##1
3. the person who's birthday is in june is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2     |   3    |
| Music-Genre   | salsa      | jazz     | r&b    |
| Birthday           | june | july | january |

