.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-1-8::.
House: modern, townhouse, colonial
The people have 3 different hobbies: camping, card-games, skydiving
1. the person who's hobby is card-games is on the right of the modern house##1
2. the colonial house is on the left of the person who's hobby is skydiving##1
3. the townhouse house is the person who's hobby is card-games##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1      |     2     |     3      |
| House    | colonial | modern | townhouse      |
| Hobby   | camping     | skydiving | card-games |

