2. the person who growsmarigold is on the far right##1
3. the person who's hobby is filmmaking is on the right of the person who's hobby is puzzles##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1    |     2      |   3    |
| Hobby   | puzzles | filmmaking | chess  |
| Flower     | zinnia     | aconite      | marigold |

