.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-1-10::.
The people's birthday is in 3 different months: june, march, january
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: adventure, comedy, zombie
1. the person watching zombie movies is on the right of the person who's birthday is in march##1
2. the person watching zombie movies is on the far right##1
3. the person watching adventure movies is on the left of the person who's birthday is in january##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |     2     |   3    |
| Birthday      | june   | march    | january    |
| Movie-Genre   | comedy | adventure | zombie |

