There are 3 different nationalities: brazilian, egyptian, nigerian
1. the person who likes coral is in the middle##1
2. the person who likes pink is on the left of the brazilian##1
3. the egyptian is on the left of the person who likes coral##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2     |    3     |
| Color   | pink    | coral     | apricot   |
| Nationality   | egyptian | brazilian | nigerian |

