.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-1-13::.
There 3 different types of food: asparagus, radish, zucchini
There are 3 different favourite beverages: juice, iced-tea, almond-milk
1. the person drinking iced-tea is on the right of the person eating asparagus##1
2. the person eating zucchini is in the middle##1
3. the person drinking juice is on the right of the person eating zucchini##1

.:: Answer ::.
|        |       1       |     2      |     3      |
| Food   | asparagus     | zucchini   | radish     |
| Beverage    | almond-milk | iced-tea | juice |

