.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-1-14::.
3 different games are played: go, monopoly, chess
3 different pets are kept: chinchilla, fish, hedgehog
1. the owner of the hedgehog is on the left of the person playing chess##1
2. the person playing chess is on the left of the person playing monopoly##1
3. the person playing monopoly is on the right of the owner of the chinchilla##1

.:: Answer ::.
|       |    1     |       2        |      3      |
| Game   | go    | chess | monopoly |
| Pet   | hedgehog | chinchilla     | fish        |

