The people grow 3 different varities of flowers: rose, sunflower, tulip
1. the person who growssunflower is on the far right##1
2. the person drinking fanta is on the right of the person drinking soy-milk##1
3. the person drinking soy-milk is on the left of the person who growstulip##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1     |   2   |   3    |
| Beverage   | soy-milk | fanta | tea    |
| Flower        | rose    | tulip | sunflower |

