.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-1-17::.
The people have 3 different jobs:  librarian, mechanic, social-worker
3 different brands of cigars are smoked: bolivar, baccarat, davidoff
1. the davidoff-smoker is on the far left##1
2. the librarian is on the far right##1
3. the bolivar-smoker is the social-worker##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |       2       |     3     |
| Job           | mechanic | social-worker | librarian |
| Cigar   | davidoff  | bolivar      | baccarat |

