.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-1-20::.
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: electronic, salsa, ambient
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: cycling, snowboarding, soccer
1. the person who's sport is snowboarding is in the middle##1
2. the person who's sport is soccer is on the left of the fan of electronic##1
3. the fan of salsa is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1    |      2       |    3    |
| Music-Genre    | ambient | electronic       | salsa  |
| Sport   | soccer  | snowboarding | cycling |

 